
'''= Belgian platform for the promotion of cooperatives'''

URL = http://febecoop.be/


=Description=

Febecoop is a platform for companies, networks and organisations from a variety of sectors to work together towards promoting, protecting and developing an alternative business-model based on cooperation. Their mains aims are to:

* promote and protect cooperative entrepreneurship
* Research and develop models of cooperative entrepreneurship
* Provide advice and guidance to develop the social and sharing economy 

